edu.stanford.nlp.mt.base

Class CoverageSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.BitSet
      • edu.stanford.nlp.mt.base.CoverageSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<Integer>

    public class CoverageSet
extends BitSet
implements Iterable<Integer>
    util.BitSet with a faster clone operation, a more readable toString() result (e.g., {1,3-6} instead of {1,3,4,5,6}), and the ability to iterate through bits set to true. Note: The BitSet iterator doesn't allow removal.
    Author:
    danielcer, Michel Galley
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
